text.paragraph:
ADD-Vantage® vials are to be constituted only with 50 or 100 mL of 5% Dextrose Injection, 0.9% Sodium Chloride Injection, or 50 mL of 0.45% Sodium Chloride Injection in ADD-Vantage® diluent (see 
                                    Instructions for Use
                                 ). ADD-Vantage® vials should be reconstituted only when it is certain that the patient is ready to receive the drug. Tazicef in ADD-Vantage® vials is stable for 24 hours at room temperature.
